62
00:03:50,700 --> 00:03:52,580
fair-skinned and quite handsome.

63
00:03:53,790 --> 00:03:55,040
Is he tall?

64
00:03:55,580 --> 00:03:57,790
He looks about 185 cm.

65
00:03:58,180 --> 00:03:59,540
- 185.
- That's 30 cm taller than you.

66
00:04:01,580 --> 00:04:03,410
- Hey, Tian.
- Good morning, Tian.

67
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:06,040
- Tian.
- Sorry.

68
00:04:06,950 --> 00:04:08,450
Hey, where is he from?

69
00:04:08,470 --> 00:04:10,450
(Ugly)

70
00:04:10,450 --> 00:04:12,750
I heard it's an international school
in Shanghai.

71
00:04:12,750 --> 00:04:13,870
An international school?

72
00:04:13,870 --> 00:04:14,950
An international school?

73
00:04:15,450 --> 00:04:17,790
High tuition, bilingual education.

74
00:04:18,370 --> 00:04:19,540
His English must be really good.

75
00:04:19,700 --> 00:04:20,950
Be careful.

76
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:23,370
Hey, Tian.

77
00:04:23,370 --> 00:04:26,290
We got a new student from Shanghai,

78
00:04:26,290 --> 00:04:27,660
and his grades are good.

79
00:04:27,910 --> 00:04:29,040
Gao Tianyang is really bad.

80
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:30,250
Watch out for your position.

81
00:04:35,410 --> 00:04:36,500
None of my business.

82
00:04:38,950 --> 00:04:39,790
So grumpy.

83
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:41,410
Handsome.

84
00:04:41,410 --> 00:04:43,790
185 cm, he should be as tall as I.

85
00:04:43,790 --> 00:04:46,950
- No.
- For real, do you know how tall you are?

86
00:04:46,950 --> 00:04:48,200
He's about...

87
00:04:48,750 --> 00:04:50,790
Twice as tall as Chili.

88
00:04:50,790 --> 00:04:52,000
Impossible.

89
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,620
- Twice as tall as Li Yu.
- Almost.

90
00:04:53,620 --> 00:04:55,160
Maybe he is as tall as Qi Jiahao.

91
00:04:55,450 --> 00:04:57,830
Wang, are you out of your mind?

92
00:04:57,830 --> 00:04:59,950
(Instructors' Office)
Why didn't you let Uncle Chen go with you?

93
00:04:59,950 --> 00:05:01,120
(Student Affairs)
No.

94
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:03,540
(Mobile phones are not allowed at school.)
I'm not out of my mind, I'm fine.

95
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:04,450
I...

96
00:05:04,450 --> 00:05:06,160
It's your first day at the new school.

97
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:08,120
It's better to have someone with you.

98
00:05:09,080 --> 00:05:10,660
- I...
- Alright, let's not talk about this.

99
00:05:10,660 --> 00:05:12,580
- How's the new school?
- It's...

100
00:05:12,580 --> 00:05:14,870
By the way, did you meet Mr. Xu?

101
00:05:16,290 --> 00:05:17,950
I'm asking if you met Mr. Xu.

102
00:05:18,370 --> 00:05:20,000
Wang, hello?

103
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,290
What do you want me to say?

104
00:05:21,290 --> 00:05:22,660
You don't give me any chance.

105
00:05:22,660 --> 00:05:24,040
No, I just want to tell you…

106
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:25,080
Who is Mr. Xu?

107
00:05:25,080 --> 00:05:26,830
Mr. Xu is the head of Student Affairs.

108
00:05:26,830 --> 00:05:28,580
He's a bit fat,

109
00:05:28,580 --> 00:05:30,750
and looks quite proper, but a bit serious.

110
00:05:30,750 --> 00:05:32,870
Mr. Xu said he would pick you up.

111
00:05:32,870 --> 00:05:34,160
You didn't see him?

112
00:05:34,160 --> 00:05:35,120
No.

113
00:05:36,160 --> 00:05:37,750
The teacher who brought me up

114
00:05:37,750 --> 00:05:39,160
was quite kind and friendly.

115
00:05:39,370 --> 00:05:40,540
He's always smiling.

116
00:05:40,540 --> 00:05:41,750
But he is talkative,

117
00:05:41,750 --> 00:05:42,830
like Paul Frank.

118
00:05:42,830 --> 00:05:43,950
That's him.

119
00:05:44,500 --> 00:05:47,330
Do you call that a serious

120
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,330
and proper look?

121
00:05:49,750 --> 00:05:52,000
Well, it's good for you

122
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:54,200
