123
00:05:54,200 --> 00:05:56,660
Sorry. I'm done talking.

124
00:05:56,660 --> 00:05:57,600
And...

125
00:05:57,600 --> 00:05:59,900
(Mobile phones are not allowed at school.)
Mobile phones are not allowed

126
00:05:59,900 --> 00:06:00,830
at school.

127
00:06:01,250 --> 00:06:02,290
Look,

128
00:06:02,290 --> 00:06:03,790
like I told you just now,

129
00:06:03,790 --> 00:06:06,450
the new student has a charming face,

130
00:06:06,450 --> 00:06:08,160
