134
00:06:13,370 --> 00:06:15,040
Theoretically?

135
00:06:15,500 --> 00:06:16,830
Are there any other textbooks?

136
00:06:17,500 --> 00:06:19,290
I've reviewed your records.

137
00:06:19,290 --> 00:06:21,000
Do you often transfer between schools?

138
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:23,080
Yes, because of my dad's job.

139
00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:24,700
I mostly followed him around.

140
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:26,620
So, you once lived in Shanghai?

141
00:06:26,620 --> 00:06:28,660
I attended an international school in Shanghai.

142
00:06:29,250 --> 00:06:32,080
No wonder you have a special accent.

143
00:06:32,080 --> 00:06:33,870
Your English must be pretty good.

144
00:06:34,290 --> 00:06:36,500
At our school,

145
00:06:36,500 --> 00:06:38,540
