147
00:06:48,620 --> 00:06:51,500
Our school has a long history for many years.

148
00:06:51,500 --> 00:06:53,200
The enrollment rate

149
00:06:53,200 --> 00:06:54,450
is particularly high.

150
00:06:54,950 --> 00:06:56,790
The Class A Grade 2 you're about to join

151
00:06:56,790 --> 00:06:59,120
