physics, chemistry.

152
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,500
Advanced class, you know?

153
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:02,290
Advanced class.

154
00:07:02,290 --> 00:07:04,330
- Yes, I know.
- It's the best.

155
00:07:04,700 --> 00:07:07,410
That is the best class for math,
physics, chemistry in the Senior Two.

156
00:07:07,950 --> 00:07:09,620
