164
00:07:26,660 --> 00:07:27,500
What?

165
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,580
I mean...

166
00:07:29,580 --> 00:07:31,790
People with the surname Jiang
are all very talented,

167
00:07:32,080 --> 00:07:33,160
