takes up a row on the Honor Roll.

170
00:07:37,330 --> 00:07:38,450
He's the top student in all subjects.

171
00:07:38,700 --> 00:07:40,040
- Yes.
- Really outstanding.

172
00:07:40,580 --> 00:07:42,290
Alright, let's move on.

173
00:07:42,290 --> 00:07:43,500
