179
00:07:58,790 --> 00:07:59,790
Dad.

180
00:08:01,450 --> 00:08:02,620
Good morning, Director.

181
00:08:03,830 --> 00:08:05,750
Come on, this seat is for you.

182
00:08:06,730 --> 00:08:07,580
