196
00:08:33,310 --> 00:08:34,430
Okay, coming.

197
00:08:34,770 --> 00:08:35,970
I'll be there right away.

198
00:08:35,970 --> 00:08:36,810
Thank you.

199
00:08:36,810 --> 00:08:40,390
He is sleeping so...

200
00:08:42,640 --> 00:08:43,720
Oh, right.

201
00:08:44,220 --> 00:08:46,350
It's your first day, so I'll make an exception.

202
00:08:46,890 --> 00:08:49,390
Starting tomorrow, no earphones,

203
00:08:49,390 --> 00:08:50,850
phones,

204
00:08:50,850 --> 00:08:52,350
